---
System Overview
Platform: HostHaven Admin Panel  
Type: Enterprise SaaS Admin Dashboard  
Architecture Pattern: Modular Monolith with Page-Based Navigation  
Routing Strategy: Nested Routes with Breadcrumb Navigation  
State Management: React Query + Context API  
Design Principles
- Page-First Design: Every major operation opens on its own dedicated page
- No Modal-Only CRUD: All create/update operations have dedicated pages
- Deep Linking: All entities support direct URL access
- Audit Trail: Every action is logged and traceable
---
Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
Role Hierarchy
Super Admin
├── Platform Admin
│   ├── Finance Admin
│   ├── Support Admin
│   └── Content Admin
├── Property Manager
│   ├── Front Desk
│   └── Housekeeping
└── Vendor Manager
    └── Vendor Staff
Role Permissions Matrix
| Module | Super Admin | Platform Admin | Finance Admin | Property Manager | Vendor Manager |
|--------|-------------|----------------|---------------|-----------------|----------------|
| Authentication | Full | Full | View | View | View |
| Dashboard | Full | Full | Full | Limited | Limited |
| Vendors | Full | Full | View | View | Self Only |
| Properties | Full | Full | View | Manage Own | View |
| Rooms | Full | Full | View | Manage Own | View |
| Bookings | Full | Full | Full | Manage Own | View |
| Services | Full | Full | View | Manage Own | Manage Own |
| Payments | Full | Full | Full | View Own | View |
| Users | Full | Limited | View | View Own | View |
| Reviews | Full | Full | View | Manage Own | Respond |
| Coupons | Full | Full | Full | Manage Own | No Access |
| Notifications | Full | Full | View | Send Own | Send Own |
| Analytics | Full | Full | Full | Limited | Limited |
| Settings | Full | Limited | Limited | Limited | No Access |
| Logs & Audits | Full | Full | View | View Own | View Own |
---
Module Breakdown
Authentication Module
Page List
| Page | Route | Purpose |
|------|-------|---------|
| Login | /auth/login | Admin login portal with multi-factor authentication |
| Forgot Password | /auth/forgot-password | Password recovery flow |
| Reset Password | /auth/reset-password/:token | Set new password via token |
| MFA Setup | /auth/mfa-setup | Configure multi-factor authentication |
| MFA Verification | /auth/mfa-verify | Verify MFA code during login |
| Session Management | /auth/sessions | View and manage active sessions |
| Login History | /auth/login-history | Audit trail of all login attempts |
CRUD Flow
Login Flow:
Login Page (/auth/login)
  ↓
[Enter Credentials]
  ↓
MFA Verification (/auth/mfa-verify) [if enabled]
  ↓
Dashboard (/dashboard)
Password Reset Flow:
Forgot Password (/auth/forgot-password)
  ↓
[Enter Email]
  ↓
Reset Password Email Sent
  ↓
Reset Password Page (/auth/reset-password/:token)
  ↓
[Set New Password]
  ↓
Login (/auth/login)
Extra Capabilities
- OAuth integration (Google, Microsoft, SAML)
- Single Sign-On (SSO) support
- IP whitelisting for admin access
- Two-factor authentication (TOTP, SMS, Email)
- Session timeout configuration
- Concurrent session limits
