Vendors Module
Page List
| Page | Route | Purpose |
|------|-------|---------|
| Vendor List | /vendors | Paginated list of all vendors with filters |
| Vendor Create | /vendors/create | Add new vendor with details and documents |
| Vendor Details | /vendors/:id | Full vendor profile and history |
| Vendor Edit | /vendors/:id/edit | Update vendor information |
| Vendor Properties | /vendors/:id/properties | Properties managed by vendor |
| Vendor Payouts | /vendors/:id/payouts | Payout history and pending payments |
| Vendor Documents | /vendors/:id/documents | License, certificates, contracts |
| Vendor Commission | /vendors/:id/commission | Commission structure and rates |
| Vendor Suspensions | /vendors/:id/suspensions | Suspension history and appeals |
| Vendor Communications | /vendors/:id/communications | Email, notes, internal messages |
CRUD Flow
Create Vendor Flow:
Vendor List (/vendors)
  ↓
[Click "Add Vendor"]
  ↓
Vendor Create (/vendors/create)
  ↓
[Step 1: Basic Information]
  ↓
[Step 2: Contact Details]
  ↓
[Step 3: Business Details]
  ↓
[Step 4: Documents Upload]
  ↓
[Step 5: Commission Setup]
  ↓
[Submit]
  ↓
Vendor Details (/vendors/:id)
Edit Vendor Flow:
Vendor Details (/vendors/:id)
  ↓
[Click "Edit"]
  ↓
Vendor Edit (/vendors/:id/edit)
  ↓
[Modify Sections]
  ↓
[Save Changes]
  ↓
Vendor Details (/vendors/:id) [updated]
Vendor Suspension Flow:
Vendor Details (/vendors/:id)
  ↓
[Click "Suspend"]
  ↓
Suspension Form Page (/vendors/:id/suspend)
  ↓
[Select Reason, Duration, Terms]
  ↓
[Confirm Suspension]
  ↓
Vendor Details (/vendors/:id) [suspended status]
Extra Capabilities
- Vendor verification workflow
- Document expiration tracking
- Automated commission calculations
- Bulk vendor imports (CSV)
- Vendor performance scoring
- Tier-based commission structures
