| Payout Settings | /payouts/settings | Payout preferences |
| Commission Report | /payments/commissions | Commission calculations |
| Refund List | /refunds | All refund requests |
| Refund Settings | /refunds/settings | Refund policies |
CRUD Flow
Manual Payment Flow:
Booking Details (/bookings/:id)
  ↓
[Click "Process Payment"]
  ↓
Payment Create (/payments/create)
  ↓
[Select Payment Method]
  ↓
[Enter Amount]
  ↓
[Process Transaction]
  ↓
Payment Details (/payments/:id)
  ↓
Booking Details (/bookings/:id) [paid status]
Refund Flow:
Booking Details (/bookings/:id)
  ↓
[Click "Refund"]
  ↓
Payment Refund (/payments/:id/refund)
  ↓
[Select Refund Amount]
  ↓
[Select Reason]
  ↓
[Confirm Refund]
  ↓
Processing...
  ↓
Payment Details (/payments/:id) [refunded status]
Payout Flow:
Payout List (/payouts)
  ↓
[Click "Create Payout"]
  ↓
Payout Create (/payouts/create)
  ↓
[Select Vendor]
  ↓
[Review Earnings]
  ↓
[Confirm Amount]
  ↓
[Process Payout]
  ↓
Payout Details (/payouts/:id)
Extra Capabilities
- Multiple payment gateway integration
- Automatic refund calculations
- Tax handling
- Multi-currency support
- Payment retry logic
- Installment payments
- Escrow management
