Route Naming Conventions
| Pattern | Example | Usage |
|---------|---------|-------|
| /module | /vendors | List page |
| /module/create | /vendors/create | Create page |
| /module/:id | /vendors/123 | Details page |
| /module/:id/edit | /vendors/123/edit | Edit page |
| /module/:id/sub-resource | /vendors/123/properties | Sub-resource list |
| /module/:id/sub-resource/:subId | /vendors/123/properties/456 | Sub-resource details |
| /module/bulk | /vendors/bulk | Bulk operations |
| /module/search | /vendors/search | Advanced search |
